# CSS Media Queries

Media queries apply styles based on screen size.

## Basic Syntax

```css
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    body {
        background-color: lightgray;
    }
}
```

## Tablet Example

```css
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
        width: 90%;
    }
}
```

## Mobile Example

```css
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .menu {
        display: none;
    }
}
```

## Real-World Example

Responsive navigation menus use media queries.

## Summary

Media queries are the foundation of responsive websites.
